{
  "name": "getSiteSdkStats",
  "description": "Get Detail Stats of a SdkClient",
  "parameters": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "site_id": {
        "example": "000000ab-00ab-00ab-00ab-0000000000ab",
        "format": "uuid",
        "type": "string"
      },
      "sdkclient_id": {
        "example": "000000ab-00ab-00ab-00ab-0000000000ab",
        "format": "uuid",
        "type": "string"
      }
    },
    "required": [
      "site_id",
      "sdkclient_id"
    ]
  },
  "handler": "http",
  "request": {
    "method": "GET",
    "url": {
      "$uri": "https://api.mist.com/api/v1/sites/{site_id}/stats/sdkclients/{sdkclient_id}"
    }
  },
  "responses": {
    "200": {
      "$encode": "markdown",
      "$block": [
        {
          "$h1": "Object"
        },
        "SDK Client Details statistics",
        "**Key properties:**",
        {
          "$ul": [
            "**id**",
            "**last_seen**: last seen timestamp",
            "**map_id**: map_id of the sdk client (if known), or null",
            "**name**: name of the sdk client (if provided)",
            [
              "**network_connection**: various network connection info for the SDK client (if known, else omitted), with RSSI in dBm, and signal level as",
              {
                "$ul": [
                  "**mac**",
                  "**rssi**",
                  "**signal_level**",
                  "**type**"
                ]
              }
            ],
            "**uuid**: uuid of the sdk client",
            "**vbeacons**: list of beacon_id’s of the sdk client is in and since when (if known)",
            "**x**: x (in pixels) of user location on the map (if known)",
            "**y**: y (in pixels) of user location on the map (if known)",
            "**zones**: list of zone_id’s of the sdk client is in and since when (if known)"
          ]
        },
        {
          "$lang": "json",
          "$code": {
            "$encode": "json",
            "$indent": true,
            "$content": {
              "$": "$.body"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    "400": {
      "$encode": "markdown",
      "$block": [
        {
          "$h1": "Object"
        },
